            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and select your destination country or region. You'll see data plans tailored to your needs, from 3GB for a quick getaway to 20GB for extended trips. I used the 10GB plan for a two-week tour of Italy, and it was more than enough for maps, emails, and social media.",
