        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After selecting a plan, complete the purchase. eSIMania sends a QR code to your email instantly. No waiting for shipping—perfect for last-minute trips. The cashback offer applied automatically, giving me 5% back on my payment.",
