      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "On your smartphone, go to Settings > Cellular > Add eSIM (for iPhone) or Settings > Network & Internet > eSIM (for Android). Scan the QR code, and the eSIM profile installs in seconds. I did this in under two minutes during a layover in Frankfurt.",
